Please help improve this article by introducing more precise citations. *(November 2018)* *(Learn how and when to remove this message)*Football club **Admiralty Rangers Football Club** is a Singaporean football club based in [Admiralty, Singapore](/wiki/Admiralty,_Singapore). The official team was formed in 2018 to take part in the [Football Association of Singapore Island Wide League](/wiki/Football_Association_of_Singapore) in order to bring the club to a higher level in Singapore football. The club made its debuting season in the FAS Island Wide League 2018. - "Members – Football Association of Singapore". *fas.org.sg*.
